 Goodness no 
 [High-Pitched Voice] 
 Rocko’s Modern Life 
 [Deep Voice] 
 Rocko’s Modern Life 
 {Silly Sound Effects} 
 [High-Pitched Voice] 
 Rocko’s Modern Life ” – Theme Song to Rocko’s Modern Life 
